## SVG TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS

- Output must be valid, production-ready SVG
- `viewBox="0 0 500 500"` for the square icon version
- All paths hand-constructed — no auto-traced fonts
- Use `<path d="...">` with precise cubic bezier curves for any curved forms
- Colors: use `#252220` as fill, `fill="currentColor"` preferred so color can be overridden via CSS
- No embedded fonts — the mark must be entirely path-based
- No strokes — filled paths only
- Must include `<title>` and `<desc>` for accessibility
- Clean, minimal SVG — no unnecessary groups, no empty elements, no Adobe Illustrator artifacts
- Include a second version: the mark centered on a `#252220` background rectangle for dark mode preview

